{"tid":2116943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"剛揭密百人斬！上原亞衣拍片…自曝「肉體變化」體重也曝光","createTime":"2020-07-20T13:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T13:11:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f88d1073232e9128f5bd6b475a7f67d8e15d983","tid":2116943,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:08:36.000Z","msg":"說到日本AV女優，老司機們都有心中的一份「D槽名單」，其中擁有「童顏巨乳」的退役女優上原亞衣，是不少人公認的女神。近期，上原除了自爆當年拍片的「百人斬秘辛」之外，近期也拍攝YouTube影片，談到自己體態轉變，並公開目前體重，吸引不少粉絲關注。<br />\n<br />\n退役多年的上原，仍然持續經營各大社群平台，並轉戰成為YouTuber。今（20日）上原就在影片中表示，自從五年前退下AV女優身分後，自己體重曾經一度爆肥超過十公斤，讓總體重來到56公斤，臉型也明顯變圓。至於為何會爆肥？上原表示由於擔任女優時期，一方面要顧及鏡頭前的體態，二方面也因為生活忙碌，不會有時間去享受自己喜歡的食物。<br />\n<br />\n就在體重一度攀升至55公斤後，上原自知這樣不行，便開始接觸健身與健康飲食，投入不少時間與心力才變回「大家熟悉的亞衣」。上原也說，自己目前體重是44.7公斤、體脂率則是17.9％，之後會繼續加油，維持好體態與自信，希望粉絲們繼續給予支持。"},{"pid":"6c5a793233c4334eeaae108594dd9c0acc38195c","tid":2116943,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/20/2674498-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2F2674498-XXL.jpg&h=c542244d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲上原自曝曾一度爆肥。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/20/2674496-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2F2674496-XXL.jpg&h=2c73f753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲上原公開體重與體脂率。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/20/2674497-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2F2674497-XXL.jpg&h=b7d6bb3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"056e22fdd19cfed2cb89f98c93f263f7e83b55bd","tid":2116943,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/24/2203220-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F24%2F2203220-XXL.jpg&h=7164c63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲上原美圖。（圖／翻攝自ai_uehara_ex IG)<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/04/2340743-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F04%2F2340743-XXL.jpg&h=9f6460a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a933a8722a04e651a3abc93345ef250a13f181a0","tid":2116943,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔知點解望到佢有D不安feel"},{"pid":"8b33d64270466893f279eb6859bbc3aa157a5ac4","tid":2116943,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}